                  <li><b>Limit Switch Malfunctions: </b>The limit switch turns off the furnace if it overheats. If this switch is faulty, it can cause the furnace to shut down prematurely or fail to shut down when necessary. We can replace defective limit switches to keep your system safe and efficient.</li>
